<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">رقم الحفظ:</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٢٣٠١١ مجاميع)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">عدد الأوراق:</span> ٢٧٥ ورقة.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">الناسخ:</span> أحمد بن بدر الحموي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
